"の制約がいくつかあります。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:55
msgid "Management cluster"
msgstr "管理クラスタ"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:56
msgid "Must have network connectivity to the target server management/BMC API"
msgstr "ターゲットサーバ管理/BMC APIへのネットワーク接続が必要"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:57
msgid ""
"Must have network connectivity to the target server control plane network"
msgstr "ターゲットサーバのコントロールプレーンネットワークへのネットワーク接続が必要"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:58
msgid ""
"For multi-node management clusters, an additional reserved IP address is "
"required"
msgstr "マルチノード管理クラスタの場合、追加の予約済みIPアドレスが必要"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:59
msgid "Hosts to be controlled"
msgstr "制御対象ホスト"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:60
msgid ""
"Must support out-of-band management via Redfish, iDRAC or iLO interfaces"
msgstr "Redfish、iDRAC、またはiLOのインタフェースを介したアウトオブバンド管理のサポー"
"トが必要"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:61
msgid ""
"Must support deployment via virtual media (PXE is not currently supported)"
msgstr "仮想メディアを使用したデプロイメントのサポートが必要(PXEは現在未サポート)"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:62
msgid ""
"Must have network connectivity to the management cluster for access to the "
"Metal<superscript>3</superscript> provisioning APIs"
msgstr ""
"Metal<superscript>3</superscript>プロビジョニングAPIにアクセスするために管理"
"クラスタへのネットワーク接続が必要"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:63
msgid ""
"Some tools are required, these can be installed either on the management "
"cluster, or on a host which can access it."
msgstr "ツールがいくつか必要です。ツールは管理クラスタにインストールするか、管理クラ"
"スタにアクセス可能なホストにインストールできます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:64
msgid ""
"<link xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/kubectl/"
"\">Kubectl</link>, <link xl:href=\"https://helm.sh\">Helm</link> and <link "
"xl:href=\"https://cluster-api.sigs.k8s.io/user/quick-start.html#install-"
"clusterctl\">Clusterctl</link>"
