"suse.com/smart/network/html/network-interface-predictable-naming/index.html\""
">Predictable Network Interface Naming</link>を有効にします。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:108 l10n/source/edge.xml:2434
msgid ""
