#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:117
msgid ""
"The output image must then be made available via a webserver, either the "
"media-server container enabled via the Metal3 chart (<xref linkend=\"metal3-"
