msgstr "静的IPの設定"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:129
msgid ""
"The BareMetalHost example above assumes DHCP provides the controlplane "
"network configuration, but for scenarios where manual configuration is "
"needed such as static IPs it is possible to provide additional "
"configuration, as described below."
msgstr ""
"上記のBareMetalHostの例では、DHCPでコントロールプレーンネットワークの設定を提"
"供することを想定していますが、静的IPなどの手動設定が必要なシナリオでは、以下"
"に説明するように追加の設定を指定できます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:130
msgid "Additional script for static network configuration"
msgstr "静的ネットワーク設定用の追加スクリプト"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:131
msgid ""
"When creating the base image with Edge Image Builder, in the "
"<literal>network</literal> folder, create the following <literal>configure-"
"network.sh</literal> file."
msgstr ""
"Edge Image Builderでゴールデンイメージを作成する際には、<literal>network</lit"
"eral>フォルダ内に次の<literal>configure-network."
"sh</literal>ファイルを作成します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:132
msgid ""
"This consumes configuration drive data on first-boot, and configures the "
"host networking using the <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/nm-"
"configurator\">NM Configurator tool</link>."
msgstr ""
"このファイルにより、初回ブート時に設定ドライブのデータを使用して、<link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/nm-configurator\">NM "
"Configuratorツール</link>を使ってホストネットワーキングを設定します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:133
msgid "Additional secret with host network configuration"
msgstr "ホストネットワーク設定の追加シークレット"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:134
msgid ""
"An additional secret containing data in the <link xl:href=\"https://nmstate."
"io/\">nmstate</link> format supported by NM Configurator (<xref "
"linkend=\"components-nmc\"/>) can be defined for each host."
msgstr ""
"NM Configurator (<xref linkend=\"components-nmc\"/>)"
"でサポートされている<link xl:href=\"https://nmstate.io/\""
">nmstate</link>形式のデータを含む追加シークレットをホストごとに定義できます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
