#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:137
msgid "BareMetalHost preparation"
msgstr "BareMetalHostの準備"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:138
msgid ""
"After creating the BareMetalHost resource and associated secrets as "
"described above, a host preparation workflow is triggered:"
msgstr "上記の説明に従ってBareMetalHostリソースと関連するシークレットを作成すると、次"
