#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1856
msgid ""
"The problem with this is that currently <literal>longhorn-single-k3s</"
"literal> and <literal>longhorn-ha-rke2</literal> are running with a Longhorn "
"version that is not compatible with any Edge release."
