#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2710
msgid ""
"Change the block <literal>RKE2ControlPlane</literal> in the <literal>capi-"
"provisioning-example.yaml</literal> shown in the following <link xl:"
"href=\"atip-automated-provisioning.xml#single-node-provision\">section</"
"link>:"
