"ラスタのバージョンを新しいバージョンに変更します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2713
msgid ""
"Change the block <literal>Metal3MachineTemplate</literal> in the "
"<literal>capi-provisioning-example.yaml</literal> shown in the following "
